== Entrances and Exits ==
=== Entrances ===
<div style="text-align: left;">
* Moving extremely fast within the Backrooms could overload the Backrooms, resulting in an unloaded area.
* A very rare error within the Backrooms could result in an unloaded area.
* There has been one unconfirmed report of a wanderer entering layer 2 through [[The Void]], who seemed to act the same way as other wanderers who have survived layer 2.
</div>
=== Exits ===
<div style="text-align: left;">
* There is only one known exit; finding an off-colored wall and simply walking through it could place a wanderer in the level that they entered layer 2 via.
* UPA supposedly showed the exit but wanderers said that it was a exit door, not a wall. It is unknown where this door leads to, or if it is even real.
</div>
